<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-qa-is-stomach-cancer-on-the-rise-in-young-adults/">Mayo Clinic Q&amp;A: Is stomach cancer on the rise in young adults?</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
