					<description><!--[CDATA[<p-->DEAR MAYO CLINIC:&nbsp;I've recently been diagnosed with inflammatory bowel disease. I'm trying to understand what IBD is and how it will affect me. Will I need surgery? ANSWER:&nbsp;Inflammatory bowel disease, or IBD, is an umbrella term for a group of chronic conditions that cause inflammation and swelling in the digestive tract. It primarily includes two […]<p></p>
